# NSJavaNeedsVirtualMachine

**Article**

Returns a Boolean value that indicates whether a Java virtual machine is required.

## Overview

Returns [doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/Swift/true] if `plist` contains a key saying that it requires Java.
